HEADWORD: Surtout
<hw>Sur*tout"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F., fr.
<ets>sur</ets> over + <ets>tout</ets> all.]</ety> <def>A man's coat to
be worn over his other garments; an overcoat, especially when long, and
fitting closely like a body coat.</def> <rj><au>Gay.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

